name: WhichAnimal
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: which animal
des: A fun game for kids: listen to the sound, then say what animal it is! Easy for cats, dogs and horses, but can you tell the difference between a lion and a bear? If you don’t know the answer, say “help” to get a hint.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
